<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>绒绒好朋友 AI 视频制作流程演示</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- 幻灯片容器 -->
    <div class="slideshow-wrapper">
      <!-- 左侧目录导航 -->
      <aside class="slide-sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-header">
          <h3>目录</h3>
        </div>
        <nav id="slide-toc" class="slide-toc"></nav>
        <div class="sidebar-footer">
          <span id="sidebar-page-counter">1 / 12</span>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <!-- 主幻灯片区域 -->
      <main class="slide-main">
        <div id="slides-container" class="slides-container"></div>

        <!-- 下方控制条 -->
        <div class="slide-controls">
          <button id="btn-prev" class="control-btn" aria-label="上一页">
            <span class="btn-arrow">←</span>
            <span id="prev-title" class="btn-title">上一页</span>
          </button>
          <div class="progress-info">
            <div class="progress-bar">
              <div id="progress-fill" class="progress-fill"></div>
            </div>
            <span id="page-counter">1 / 12</span>
          </div>
          <button id="btn-next" class="control-btn" aria-label="下一页">
            <span id="next-title" class="btn-title">下一页</span>
            <span class="btn-arrow">→</span>
          </button>
        </div>
      </main>
    </div>

    <!-- 图片灯箱 -->
    <div id="image-lightbox" class="lightbox" aria-hidden="true">
      <button id="lightbox-close" class="lightbox-close" type="button">✕</button>
      <img id="lightbox-image" alt="预览图" />
      <p id="lightbox-caption"></p>
    </div>

    <div id="ai-script-modal" class="ai-script-modal" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="ai-script-modal-dialog" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-label="AI 梳理后的初版分镜脚本">
        <header class="ai-script-modal-header">
          <div>
            <h3>AI 梳理后的初版分镜脚本</h3>
            <p>由 AI 根据原始故事想法整理生成，作为后续人工修改的基础</p>
          </div>
          <button id="ai-script-modal-close" class="ai-script-close" type="button" aria-label="关闭弹窗">✕</button>
        </header>
        <section id="ai-script-modal-body" class="ai-script-modal-body"></section>
        <footer class="ai-script-modal-footer">
          <p>AI 输出的分镜脚本不是最终稿，而是帮助设计师快速搭建结构。最终镜头是否成立，仍然需要人工判断和修改。</p>
          <button id="ai-script-modal-close-footer" class="doc-btn secondary" type="button">关闭</button>
        </footer>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="storyboard-extended-modal" class="ai-script-modal" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="ai-script-modal-dialog" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-label="人工调整后的分镜脚本">
        <header class="ai-script-modal-header">
          <div>
            <h3>人工调整后的分镜脚本</h3>
            <p>基于 AI 初版分镜，由设计师逐镜头修改和延展形成</p>
          </div>
          <button id="storyboard-modal-close" class="ai-script-close" type="button" aria-label="关闭弹窗">✕</button>
        </header>
        <section id="storyboard-extended-modal-body" class="ai-script-modal-body"></section>
        <footer class="ai-script-modal-footer">
          <p>AI 生成的是分镜骨架，人工延展才是可执行分镜。设计师需要根据画面逻辑、动作可生成性和剪辑节奏继续调整。</p>
          <button id="storyboard-modal-close-footer" class="doc-btn secondary" type="button">关闭</button>
        </footer>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script src="script.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
